    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Fragmented HR Policy Management and Reactive Decision-Making"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "It manages a large workforce operating within a highly regulated environment. While HR policies were documented and accessible, the organization struggled to manage policy understanding, feedback, and updates in a structured and scalable way."
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "FACING SIMILAR CHALLENGES?",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "This company manages a large workforce operating within a highly regulated environment. While HR policies were documented and accessible, the organization struggled to manage policy understanding, feedback, and updates in a structured and scalable way."
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "As a result, HR teams spent a significant amount of time handling repetitive, low-value tasks instead of focusing on strategic initiatives."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Key Business Areas Impacted Included:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Employee experience and confidence"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Repeated questions and unclear policies reduced employee trust and clarity."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "HR operational efficiency"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Manual handling of queries, feedback, and updates consumed excessive HR time."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Policy governance and compliance"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Informal feedback, delayed approvals, and manual change tracking increased governance"
        }
      ],
