      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Impact & Outcomes"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The implementation of agentic AI with Microsoft Copilot Studio transformed the company's HR policy management into a real-time, self-service asset—delivering measurable operational efficiency and improved employee engagement across the organization."
        },
        {
          "t": "img",
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/impact-outcomes.webp",
          "w": 175,
          "h": 150,
          "alt": ""
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Faster, proactive query resolution through automated self-service handling of HR policy-related questions."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Elimination of manual effort, freeing HR teams to move away from administrative tasks and focus on strategic initiatives."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Stronger operational control with a fully governed workflow and enhanced policy clarity."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Improved employee satisfaction via a feedback-driven system that directly boosts Employee Net Promoter Scores (NPS)."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Better agility and compliance through accelerated policy update turnaround times and continuous monitoring."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Aligned business execution by maintaining full control over HR workflows while ensuring regulatory compliance."
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "As a result, the company gained a unified, intelligent performance monitoring platform that improved agility, strengthened HR governance, and reinforced their position as a forward-thinking leader in the industry."
        }
      ],
